snippet.title: Zendaya & Tom Holland Reunite For Dinner Date In Paris After Confirming Romance
snippet.description:
Zendaya & Tom Holland Reunite For Dinner Date In Paris After Confirming Romance

#Zendaya #TomHolland #SpiderMan

Zendaya Maree Stoermer Coleman is an American actress and singer. She is the recipient of numerous accolades, including a Primetime Emmy Award, a Satellite Award, and a Saturn Award. Zendaya began her career as a child model and backup dancer.

Thomas Stanley Holland is an English actor. A graduate of the BRIT School for Performing Arts and Technology in London, he began his acting career on London stage in the title role of Billy Elliot the Musical in the West End theatre from 2008 to 2010.

With Spider-Man's identity now revealed, our friendly neighborhood web-slinger is unmasked and no longer able to separate his normal life as Peter Parker from the high stakes of being a superhero.
